%% Data Flow Diagram: Model Metadata Collection
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant Tekton as Tekton Pipeline<br/>(Konflux CI/CD)
    participant Extractor as model-extractor CLI<br/>(Go Binary)
    participant HF as HuggingFace API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Registry as registry.redhat.io<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant FS as Local Filesystem<br/>/app/data
    participant Build as Container Build<br/>Dockerfile.konflux
    participant ImgReg as Container Registry<br/>quay.io
    participant Dashboard as RHOAI Dashboard<br/>(Runtime Consumer)

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Tekton,ImgReg: Flow 1: CI/CD Catalog Generation (Build Time)

        Tekton->>Extractor: Execute model-extractor

        Extractor->>HF: GET /api/collections (RedHat AI)<br/>TLS 1.2+, No Auth (public)
        HF-->>Extractor: Model collections list

        loop For each model in collection
            Extractor->>HF: GET /api/models/{model}<br/>TLS 1.2+, No Auth
            HF-->>Extractor: Model details + README
        end

        Extractor->>Registry: GET /v2/{repo}/manifests<br/>TLS 1.2+, Registry credentials
        Registry-->>Extractor: OCI manifests + timestamps

        loop For each model image
            Extractor->>Registry: GET /v2/{repo}/blobs/{layer}<br/>TLS 1.2+, Registry credentials
            Registry-->>Extractor: Model card layer data
        end

        Note over Extractor: Enrichment: Match registry models<br/>to HuggingFace via similarity scoring

        Note over Extractor: Generate YAML catalogs:<br/>models-catalog.yaml<br/>validated-models-catalog.yaml<br/>other-models-catalog.yaml

        Extractor->>FS: Write catalog YAML files<br/>to /app/data

        Build->>FS: COPY catalog files into container
        Build->>ImgReg: Push multi-arch image<br/>(amd64, arm64, ppc64le, s390x)<br/>TLS 1.2+, Konflux SA auth
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over Dashboard,FS: Flow 2: Runtime Data Consumption

        Dashboard->>FS: Volume mount /app/data (read-only)
        FS-->>Dashboard: models-catalog.yaml<br/>validated-models-catalog.yaml<br/>other-models-catalog.yaml
        Note over Dashboard: Display AI model catalog to users
    end
